name: 人造人間 V O I D
description: A very early example of my glitch work, posted to Tumblr on October 30, 2014. This period is pre-watermark and before I incorporated animated subjects in my pieces, but the foundation of what would become the style I'm known for is all there. 640x600 pixels, 724.85 KB, 30 frames. Original 2014 post ---> https://n-lite.tumblr.com/post/101356753620/%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%A0%E4%BA%BA%E9%96%93-v-o-i-d
